1 Henry Gustler (Gusler) Morris (b.3 Dec 1798-District of Columbia; d.6 Nov 1875-Monroe Co., Ohio)  Bible, Morris Cemetery

... + Mary Kinkade (b. 1 Feb 1804; d. 9 Oct 1865-Monroe Co., Ohio)  Bible, tombstone

 

Although she diligently researched all the families of Henry Gustler Morris and Mary Kinkade, Allie "Elizabeth" Morris Hinton (1920-2012), a descendant of David Charles Morris, paved the basis for this Indiana branch of the Henry Gustler Morris tree.  Her 35 years of research, without help of the internet,  and hours spent  in cemeteries--her overwhelming dedication is much appreciated by those of us left to add on to our Morris  tree.
